<h2 class="bold font-l">My Mom is My Wife! Go USA!</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In both Tina's and Bob's stories, Gene insists that his wife be played by Linda. The others find it questionable, while Linda finds it sweet. </p>
</div>
</div>
